detail.name: Hell's Flash
detail.effect: [Activate Battle][Your Turn] Your cards with 《Android》 in their special traits that are in a battle with your opponent's Battle Cards get +25000 power for the battle.

detail.name: ヘルズフラッシュ
detail.effect: 【起動 戦闘中】【自分のターン中】相手のバトルカードと戦闘中の自分の特徴《人造人間》を持つカードは、この戦闘中、パワー+25000。
